3) Data Visualisation in Looker Studio (Chicago Crime Dashboard)¶

  • Overview: From 2017 to 2021, total Chicago crime cases were 1.2 millions with arrest rate 18.17%. Almost one out of five cases has been solved. A significant drop of cases was noticed since 2020.
  • Time Trend: More cases occurred before COVID (2017 to 2019), during hot seasons (spring, autumn) and in the day (6am to 8pm)
  • Hotspots: Theft and criminal damage often occur on the streets while battery mostly happened in apartments and residence areas.

Conclusion: Foreigners may enquire safety information from city councils or police before moving into a new area.

Project Link: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1AH5IQB3gMKzf544mGUa4Fd9loobZQ_WG/view?usp=sharing

4) Web Scraping, Natural Langauge Processing, Sentiment Analysis (Restaurant Review Analysis)¶

  • Scrap data from webpage using Beautiful Soup
  • Perform natural language processing on Review data
  • Analyze sentiment of Review data using nltk.sentiment

Conclusion: Review sentiments have weak positive correlation to the rating from Tripadvisor users. This indicates that a single rating can not represent user's full expression and review sentiments should be taken into consideration when picking a restaurant.

Project Link: https://liewjiaton96.github.io/DataScience/Restaurant_Review_Analysis
